<section class='callout'>
  <p>
    “Estamos orientados a satisfacer a todos aquellos que buscan cervezas
    artesanales de origen sustentable que aportan sabores, aromas, colores
    naturales y con procesos amigables con nuestro medioambiente.”
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .callout {
    display: grid;
    align-items: center;
    background:
      linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)),
      url("/imgs/beercup-desktop.webp") center / cover no-repeat;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .callout p {
    font-family: "Beth Ellen", cursive;
    font-size: 3.7rem;
    color: #ffffff;
    line-height: 80px;
    padding: 40px;
    text-align: center;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  /* media queries */

  @media screen and (min-width: 761px) {
    .callout p {
      font-size: 5rem;
      line-height: 115px;
      top: 2500px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 880px) {
    .callout {
      background-image: linear-gradient(
          to right,
          rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5),
          rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)
        ),
        url("/imgs/beercup-mobile.webp");
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .callout p {
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      line-height: 49px;
      padding: 15px 30px;
    }
  }
</style>
